Release 1.0.2 - 2013-04-05

TypeChangesBy

Now this module uses mega-mapper (added dependency) to retrieve PDB xrefs from there and replace the ones coming from UniProt, which include theoretical models. The previous solution was buggy, as it retrieved PDB xrefs for all of the orthologs, mixing them and resulting sometimes in the wrong thumbnail being displayed. Fixes 146.rafalcan

Updated to latest version of parent pom file (move to GitHub), ep-domain, ep-util, uniprotjapi - to use always the latest release - and junit.rafalcan
